", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2208}, {\"ngram\": \"the leaderboard\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2227}, {\"ngram\": \"par\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was pretty emotional.\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am representing Australia, which is weird, I guess.\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2289, \"end\": 2298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9935694389935193, \"rank\": 0.006472118145821737, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not know I was going to react like that.\\\"\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His teammate Jason Day had not represented Australia since he was an amateur 20 years ago.\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2387, \"end\": 2396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Day\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0947208491103412e-72, \"text\": \"Jason Day\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Day\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Day\"}, {\"begin\": 2417, \"end\": 2426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9935694389935193, \"rank\": 0.006472118145821737, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His teammate\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2386}, {\"ngram\": \"an amateur\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The emotion, it caught me off guard.\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"guard\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It took me a few holes to get over it.\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few holes\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This week we are not playing for money, we are playing for medals.\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2608, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2580}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2607}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the most nervous I have felt standing on a tee in a long time.\\\"\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tee\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2660}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Golf has endured a troubled relationship with the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2743, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Golf\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2683}, {\"ngram\": \"a troubled relationship\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was first held 50 miles north of here in Compiegne in 1900 and was played again in 1904.\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2788, \"end\": 2797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Compi\\u00e8gne\", \"score\": 0.9989184438554329, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Compiegne\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Compi\\u00e8gne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Compi\\u00e8gne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was boycotted in 1908, cancelled in 1920 and not played again until the 2016Olympicsin Rio de Janeiro.\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2016Olympicsin Rio de Janeiro\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 2944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the intervening years, golf developed its own identity, with a rich history and a particular sense of prestige and finicky personality.\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 3085, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the intervening years\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2971}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2977}, {\"ngram\": \"its own identity\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 3004}, {\"ngram\": \"a rich history\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"a particular sense\", \"from\": 3030, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"prestige and finicky personality\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It created its own distinct culture built partly around exclusion which did not necessarily chime with the Olympic ideal.\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3207, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its own distinct culture\", \"from\": 3097, \"to\": 3121}, {\"ngram\": \"exclusion\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3151}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic ideal\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When it was reinstated for Rio, most of the best male players rejected invitations, citing concerns over the Zika virus or pointing to their busy schedules.\", \"from\": 3209, \"to\": 3365, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3236, \"end\": 3239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997484167976298, \"rank\": 0.00025164651222670594, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best male players\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3270}, {\"ngram\": \"invitations\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3291}, {\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3308}, {\"ngram\": \"the Zika virus\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3328}, {\"ngram\": \"their busy schedules\", \"from\": 3344, \"to\": 3364}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The top four in the world rankings that year - Jason Day, Dustin Johnson, Jordan Spieth and Rory McIlroy - all said no.\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3485, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3391}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't much different in Tokyo which played out without fans and some star names missing too.\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3515, \"end\": 3520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.8731917893631623, \"rank\": 0.14521820326467855, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3550}, {\"ngram\": \"some star names\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's right in the middle of a big stretch of golf for me,\\\" Johnson said when asked to explain why he would not be there, as if the Olympics were another sport entirely.\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3644, \"end\": 3651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.9912281252040701, \"rank\": 0.0062938316495456045, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3609}, {\"ngram\": \"a big stretch\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3626}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3634}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3712, \"to\": 3724}, {\"ngram\": \"another sport\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this Games has not been shunned by the players and that enthusiasm has been reciprocated by fans.\", \"from\": 3755, \"to\": 3856, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this Games\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3769}, {\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 3794, \"to\": 3805}, {\"ngram\": \"that enthusiasm\", \"from\": 3810, \"to\": 3825}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from